User max.gautier@objectif-libre.com
PassCmd "oauth2get gmail work"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs XOAUTH2

IMAPStore gmail-work
Account gmail-work

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/work/
Inbox ~/Mail/work

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-work:
Near :gmail-local:
# Automatically create missing mailboxes on server only
Create Far
Patterns INBOX archives kubernetes openstack
# Save the synchronization state files in the relevant directory
SyncState *

Channel gmail-special-folders
Far ":gmail-work:[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Near :gmail-local:sent
Create Near
SyncState *

